{"tid":799148,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強：城鎮污水設施建設蘊藏著巨大投資潛力","createTime":"2018-08-30T00:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T04:48:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9c73d1be1ade7d39ded60ea263a8a3e6cb183086","tid":799148,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://plib.aastocks.com/aafnnews/image/medialib/20171020174438819_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplib.aastocks.com%2Faafnnews%2Fimage%2Fmedialib%2F20171020174438819_m.jpg&h=85135b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《中國政府網》公布，總理李克強日前主持召開國務院西部地區開發領導小組會議時表示，中國當前仍處於城鎮化進程中，城鎮化率僅有58%左右，而城鎮污水設施建設是城鎮化建設基礎的基礎，其中蘊藏著巨大的投資潛力，特別對西部地區城鎮化建設來說，城鎮污水、垃圾處理設施建設等是短板中的短板。李克強要求有關部門牽頭，積極參考地方經驗做法，研究推進城鎮污水、垃圾處理設施建設。<br />\n<br />\n李克強指出，使用污水處理或垃圾回收服務，首先要轉變處理收費的觀念，目前城市人群已經普遍接受這種觀念，否則不可持續。同時要不斷創新投資運營機制，吸引民間資本參與，充分發揮市場作用，多措並舉完善污水處理收費制度。(ta/w)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.892633/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.892633%2F1&d=Zv7mRUQtUzp1GiUzrZYPedZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=cdce3433\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.892633/1</a>"},{"pid":"6da1f665f4722e9215516f0dbbb138bd6fa200a6","tid":799148,"uid":156772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:03:42.000Z","msg":"短板中的短板即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692929a1632dcd857574d7a3f71b03201643941a","tid":799148,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:18:34.000Z","msg":"環境保護一帶一路<br />\n<br />\n環境保護大開發<br />\n<br />\n環境保護自貿區<br />\n<br />\n正式上線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8fef23e6789c2fa603ac5297d4a187a0e9f649","tid":799148,"uid":189638,"like":3,"dislike":0